\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li260\sl324\slmult1\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 The generated output must be suitable for scientific publication, with consistent layout, proportions, and clean graphics, but implementation can remain simple for MVP.\
